  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<h1 dir=\"ltr\">Nagging Doubt SPELL 2</h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">[Dynamic Heightening][Emotion][Enchantment][Mental]</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Traditions occult, divine</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cast [two-actions] somatic, verbal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Range 30 feet; Target 1 creature</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Duration sustained</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The target is plagued with thoughts of their past failings, or what they may have forgotten. Did they leave the stove on? They make a Will saving throw at the start of their turn for as long as this spell endures.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Critical Success</strong> The spell ends for this creature.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes 1d6 mental damage.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Failure </strong>The creature is</p>\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\">@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1}</h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">slowed 1, losing an action this turn. The creature takes 2d6 mental damage.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is slowed 1 for as long as the spell endures without further saving throws. The creature takes 2d6 mental damage.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The spell can target another creature within range.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The range of the spell increases by 30 feet.</p>\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-1f3f3ff1-7fff-9623-1143-ac5da30f824b\">Heightened (+1) </strong>Increase the damage by 1d6.</p>",
